    public class SeLionSelendroidDriver
extends io.selendroid.client.SelendroidDriver
implements SeLionAndroidBridgeDriver
    SeLionSelendroidDriver provides facility to add custom CommandExecutor to SelendroidDriver. This class also implements the SeLionAndroidBridgeDriver interface to expose methods for UiObject and its subclasses.
